# CppSerialPort
A simple cross platform class for accessing serial ports (COM1 or /dev/ttyACM0, etc) and network sockets (UDP, TCP)

This repository includes two command line applications (CppSerialPortChaiScriptNetworkClient and CppSerialPortChaiScriptSerialPortClient) that exports the CppSerialPort namespace into ChaiScript (http://chaiscript.com).
It can be built by specifying:
    -DWITH_CHAISCRIPT:BOOL=ON
as an argument to install.sh or CMakeLists.txt directly.

